, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/40752986adba6d171181c7f22370d105-kix.e7detffz6jbn-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>作为Brave Group APAC针对东南亚和泰语地区的VTuber制作“ <a href="https://astars-production.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">AStars Production</a> ”的首个项目，四人组合“ <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@AStarsofficial" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chrono</a> Prince”已首次亮相。</p><p> “时空王子”是以“来自不同世界和时代的王子”为概念的单位。成员有<a href="https://x.com/Bishamon_AS/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">黑猫毗沙门</a>、<a href="https://x.com/RionChitose_AS/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">千岁理音</a>、<a href="https://x.com/AkiMasamune_AS/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">正宗亚纪</a>、<a href="https://x.com/YukitoHoshi_AS/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">星时行人</a>。</p><p>作为小分队的出道歌曲，原曲MV将于7月25日（周四）20:00起在官方YouTube频道公开。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[原创歌曲预告]《Chrono Prince》完整MV将于2024年7月25日18:00发布#AStars_VTuber" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cNYb5I1iCbI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000356.000044525.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">勇敢集团有限公司新闻稿</a></p><h2>Nijisanji x 《PUBG MOBILE》合作举行</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/40752986adba6d171181c7f22370d105-kix.44qul9lbr9vg-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/40752986adba6d171181c7f22370d105-kix.44qul9lbr9vg-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/40752986adba6d171181c7f22370d105-kix.44qul9lbr9vg-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/40752986adba6d171181c7f22370d105-kix.44qul9lbr9vg-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/40752986adb